data.description: Seller was re-relocated before he could move into this stunning Saxony by Shaddock Home on 70' lot! Bring your pickiest buyers to see this great home with large kitchen, double ovens + microwave, big quartz island, master and 2nd bedroom downstairs, two story family room that looks onto big covered patio. Hardwood floors in entry, walkway, family room, kitchen and breakfast rooms. All bedrooms except downstairs guest room have walk in closets. HUGE laundry room, walk-in pantry with extra space for storage, and built-in mudroom off the hallway to the second garage. Kitchen has 5 gas burners, vented hood, under cabinet lighting and backsplash. Split garage makes for great storage. Walk down the street to amenity center, community pool and greenbelt. Great corner lot in cul-de-sac location. Stone turret. Seller's loss is buyer's gain!
